  - expression: Default
    text: Here, you can <color=yellow>fuse</color> your heroes together to create
      a stronger hero.
  - expression: 
    text: Heroes have three <color=blue>tiers</color>. You can only fuse together
      heroes of the same <color=blue>tier</color>.
  - expression: 
    text: Fusing two heroes together will produce a single hero which is <color=blue>one
      level higher</color>.
